This package is free software; you can redistribute it and/or modify it 
under the same terms as Perl itself.

                                   ***

Two main modules and several submodules are contained.  For more details
read following POD documentation:

    CSS::Janus - Converts a left-to-right Cascading Style Sheet (CSS) into a right-to-left one
    CSS::Yamaantaka - Converts direction of Cascading Style Sheet (CSS)

For more details about the utility program cssflip, run:

    cssflip --help

$$
